cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper deals with processing high-dimensional datasets and reducing their dimensionality, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and signal processing (cs.SI). The applications mentioned in the abstract, such as segmentation of images and videos, detection of vehicles and vascular vessels, and characterization of materials, are all related to these sub-categories. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
